---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Personalized Plate Painting"
  description="Create custom painted dinnerware pieces in Centerville, TN. Perfect personalized gifts!"
  price="$15-20"
  duration="1-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="personalized plates, custom dinnerware, pottery painting plates, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Personalized Plate Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Design and paint beautiful personalized dinner plates or decorative dinnerware at Made @ The Local. Create custom plates that are both functional art pieces and meaningful gifts.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Select from our high-quality ceramic plates and design your custom decoration. Whether you're painting family initials, anniversary dates, decorative patterns, or artistic designs, you have complete creative control. Our instructors help with technique and offer suggestions, but your vision comes to life. We professionally glaze and kiln-fire your plates so they're dishwasher-safe and durable. Perfect for special occasions, custom gifts, or decorative display pieces.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Quality ceramic plate(s) to personalize</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints and colors</li>
      <li>Painting brushes and supplies</li>
      <li>Design guidance from instructors</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Dishwasher-safe finished plates</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Wedding gifts or anniversaries</li>
      <li>Custom family name plates</li>
      <li>Holiday or seasonal dinnerware</li>
      <li>Personalized gifts for special occasions</li>
      <li>Decorative wall plates</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your plate and design idea (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your custom design (45-60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final touches and glazing (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Professional kiln-firing for durability</li>
      <li>Pick up finished plates in 2 weeks</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $15-20<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Create your personalized plates!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made custom anniversary plates as a gift. They were absolutely beautiful! Our friends thought they were professionally made!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Robert & Linda</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Created personalized family plates for our Thanksgiving table. So special and meaningful!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Margaret J.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"This was my wedding gift to friends. They use them regularly and always talk about how much they love them!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Nicole K.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hand-Painted Mug Creation</h3>
        <p>Paint your own coffee mug - the perfect personal keepsake.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/hand-painted-mug-creation" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint Your Own Pottery Session</h3>
        <p>Choose from pre-made pottery pieces and paint them your way.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/paint-your-own-pottery-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pottery Bowl Painting Session</h3>
        <p>Paint beautiful ceramic bowls to add to your collection.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/pottery-bowl-painting-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
